---
title: Indian Prawn & Roast Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice
description: Dive in the deep end of flavour with a prawn curry that will leave you feeling refreshed and satisfied. The rich tamarind and curry aromas fill up the bowl and a fluffy garlic rice finishes it off. Your tastebuds will be leaping with joy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65b1ad53553f74890680db85-99d20528.jpeg
